attributes.name: Pomegranate 1:1 CBD + Hybrid Enhanced Gummies 100:100mg
attributes.body:
We’ve taken the best of both worlds with our Pomegranate 1:1 THC:CBD gummies. They are a great compliment to any adventure by providing a balanced and enjoyable high for both mind and body using a Hybrid terpene blend. If you are new or sensitive to edibles, the Pomegranate gummies are an excellent place to start. Have some before getting into your yoga routine, or climbing to the highest peak.


It’s a little like getting a high five from your imaginary friend. Enjoy!


100mg THC:100mg CBD per package, 10mg THC:10mg CBD per gummy.


Contains: Coconut

attributes.name: KulluKush 1 Gram Tank - Strawberry Cough
attributes.body:
Introducing the Kullukush 1 gram Tank in the Strawberry Cough strain from Multitude Manufacturing. This tank is filled with a premium filtered distillate with over 90 percent THC potency and infused with a custom blend of live and botanical terpenes. KulluKush tanks are designed to provide you with a convenient and enjoyable cannabis experience. It's the pinnacle of potency and quality with the Kullukush Tank in the high-end I-Krusher ceramic reservoir.

Known for its cerebral, energizing, and euphoric effects, this tank offers a delightful combination of berry, strawberry, and sweet flavors. With each puff, you'll experience a smooth and flavorful vapor that captures the essence of this popular strain.

attributes.body:
